import { Grid, Link, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

export const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{height: "30vh", backgroundColor: "#000", color: "#fff"}}>
        <Grid container sx={{display: "flex", justifyContent: "space-around", padding: "3.123rem"}}>
            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Acerca de Nosotros</Typography>
                <Box sx={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "column"}}>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Quiénes somos</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Sala de prensa</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Sostenibilidad</Link>
                </Box>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Información legal</Typography>

                <Box sx={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "column"}}>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Términos de uso</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Conoce tus derechos</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Devolución de tasas de embarque</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Condiciones de contrato de transporte</Link>
                </Box>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Explorar</Typography>
                <Box sx={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "column"}}>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Prepara tu viaje</Link>
                    <Link href="#" underline="hover">Destinos</Link>
                </Box>
                
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}
